org.epics.pvData.misc
Interface LinkedList<T>

public interface LinkedList<T>

Linked List with user supplied storage for node. The user must create nodes by calling LinkedListCreate.createNode. A node can be put on any LinkedList but only on one list at a time. It is the users responsibility to synchronize access to the list.

Author:
mrk
